                    <li>Upload all THREE PDF files:
                        <ul>
                            <li>[lastName firstName] Brand Kit.pdf</li>
                            <li>[lastName firstName] Proposal.pdf</li>
                            <li>[lastName firstName] Flyer.pdf</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Verify all three files are attached</li>
                    <li>Click "Turn in"</li>
                    <li>Confirm submission</li>
                </ol>

                <div class="info-box success">
                    <p><strong>Before You Submit:</strong> Open each PDF to verify it looks correct and is the right file. Once submitted, you cannot edit unless you "unsubmit" (which may count as late).</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Deadline & Late Policy</h3>
                <p>All three files must be submitted by the end of Day 2 class period. Late submissions will follow the standard course late work policy as outlined in the syllabus.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
